title: Tin Foil Hat Ep 28: Eddie Bravo Goes Off!
description:
Welcome to another episode of Tin Foil Hat with Sam Tripoli! This episode, Ryan and Sam, welcome Eddie Bravo back to the show for the most Eddie Bravo podcast you will ever hear. This episode we discuss....
1) The Illumanti
2) Space
3) North Korea
4) Nuclear Weapons that may or may not exist
5)Is Alex Jones
